ready to give up on us yet.

09:30.673 --> 09:31.906
- My God.
- What?

09:31.908 --> 09:33.241
- You have to hide.
- Why?

09:33.243 --> 09:35.076
- Quick, it's Cole.
- Fuck that.

09:35.078 --> 09:36.543
- No, please, go in the back.
- I'm not hiding from him.

09:36.545 --> 09:37.845
