- Hey.

10:24.291 --> 10:26.390
Can I come in?

10:26.392 --> 10:29.060
Yeah. Yeah, come in.

10:36.435 --> 10:37.801
You okay?

10:37.803 --> 10:39.903
Yeah, I think so. Are you?

10:39.905 --> 10:41.972
No. Not really.

10:41.974 --> 10:45.008
No. No, no, no, no. Me neither, I'm...

10:45.010 --> 10:47.410
- What were we thinking?
- Yeah, right, I know.

10:47.412 --> 10:48.745
