11:03.995 --> 11:05.661
- And what about you?
- Right.

11:05.663 --> 11:07.596
You've come so far putting
your life back together.

11:07.598 --> 11:11.466
I do not want something
like this to derail you.

11:11.468 --> 11:12.834
