11:12.836 --> 11:15.603
Yeah, I-I don't want to derail the prog...

11:15.605 --> 11:18.106
What, you think I'm gonna freak out again?

11:18.108 --> 11:20.275
That's... no. I-I just...

11:20.277 --> 11:21.676
